channel.description:
[u]Difficulty - 1/10
Things you need to have in your source:[/u] Client.java, Npchandler.java, Autospawn.cfg, Player.java, Wearing.java

Simple Skill I made where you type the command to go there and you have to kill a certain amount of the first monster to move on to the next stage. There's 4 stages, You can add more if you want.

[size=12pt][u][b]Step 1:[/b][/u][/size]
Client.java
Right under "public class client extends Player implements Runnable {" add...
[code]public void caveing() {
if(!isInCaveing1() && !isInCaveing2() && !isInCaveing3() && !isInCaveing4()) {
caveingstage = 0;
kills1 = 0;
kills2 = 0;
kills3 = 0;
kills4 = 0;
boss1 = 0;
boss2 = 0;
boss3 = 0;
} else {
if(caveingstage == 1 && kills1 == 10) {
addSkillXP(75000, 21);
sM("Congratz! You've Completed Stage 1!");
sM("You need to kill 5 black dragons to Continue!");
caveingstage = 2;
kills1 = 0;
toX = 2709;
toY = 9485;
heightLevel = 0;
}
if (caveingstage == 2 && kills2 == 5) {
addSkillXP(150000, 21);
sM("Congratz! You've Conpleted Stage 2!");
sM("You need to kill 2 KBD's to continue!");
caveingstage = 3;
kills2 = 0;
toX = 2705;
toY = 9522;
heightLevel = 0;
}
if (caveingstage == 3 && kills3 == 2) {
addSkillXP(200000, 21);
sM("Congratz! You've Conpleted Stage 3!");
sM("You need to kill all 3 Boss's to continue!");
sM("Each boss is located in a different tunnel!");
caveingstage = 4;
kills3 = 0;
toX = 2705;
toY = 9522;
heightLevel = 0;
}
if (caveingstage == 4 && kills4 == 3) {
cwin += 1;
addSkillXP(575000, 21);
addItem(995, 250000000);
sM("CONGRATULATIONS! You've Beaten Caveing "+ cwin +" times!");
sM("You've won 1,000,000 exp during all stages.");
sM("For Completeing it all, You also win 250mil!");
toX = 3213;
toY = 3424;
heightLevel = 0;
}
}
}[/code]

