-[size=12pt][b]THINGS I LEFT OUT OF THE TUTORIAL THAT YOU NEED TO DO BELOW[/b][/size]-
In Player.java search for "public int playerRunecrafting = 20;" and under it add
[code]	public int playerCaveing = 21;[/code]

Also in Wearing.java find "public int GetCLRunecrafting(int ItemID) {" and under
[code]	if (ItemName.startsWith("Runecrafting hood")) {
			return 99;
		}
		return 1;
	}[/code]
add
[code]		public int GetCLCaveing(int ItemID) {
		if (ItemID == -1) {
			return 1;
		}
		String ItemName = GetItemName(ItemID);
		if (ItemName.startsWith("Caveing cape")) {
			return 99;
		}
		if (ItemName.startsWith("Caveing hood")) {
			return 99;
		}
		return 1;
	}[/code]

And your done!!!
